    <id>desktop_workspace</id>
    <name>Desktop Workspace</name>
    <summary>Open Nextcloud apps in a desktop-style workspace.</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[Desktop Workspace adds a browser-contained workspace to Nextcloud with app windows, a taskbar, app pinning, desktop icons, saved window/app-menu/icon state, and optional desktop-folder/file-manager features.

Admins can enable the app like any other Nextcloud app and configure decorations, the experimental file manager, multiple-window behavior, and per-user resets from the Desktop Workspace admin settings. Users can adjust their own desktop icons, desktop folder, decoration, experimental opt-ins, window state, and reset options from the Desktop personal settings.]]></description>
